gher-temperature superconductors and for the estimation of $\\lambda$ from\nexperimental data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2021 17:20:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Jun 2021 22:55:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 10 Jul 2021 19:33:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-13"}
