ization condition and the imposed\nasymptotic behavior depend on the effective mass of the perturbations, and\ntherefore the selected vacuum state varies in the presence of the scalar field\npotential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jun 2021 10:11:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Nov 2021 03:57:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-23"}
