he crucial role played by the (possibly\ndifferent) models used to compute the base forecasts, we re-interpret the CCC\nreconciliation of Hollyman et al. (2021) as a forecast pooling approach,\nshowing that accuracy improvement may be gained by adopting a simple forecast\naveraging strategy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jun 2021 10:50:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-11"}
