ifier and 0.99 for the Random Forest (RF)\nclassifier. The feature extraction algorithm developed in this work and the RF\nclassifier algorithm is suitable for embedded applications, for example in\ninspection drones, as long as they are highly accurate and computationally\nlight, both in terms of memory and processing time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jun 2021 14:02:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-11"}
